    <item>
      <title>加密货币“混合器”因洗钱被判 12 年半监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/crypto-mixer-gets-150-months-for-bitcoin-fog-money-laundering</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币混合服务公司 Bitcoin Fog 的创始人因从贩卖非法毒品的暗网市场洗钱数千万美元，被判处 12 年半监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/crypto-mixer-gets-150-months-for-bitcoin-fog-money-laundering</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 22:42:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币“混合器”因比特币洗钱被判有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/crypto-mixer-convicted-of-money-laundering-on-bitcoin-fog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加密货币混合服务公司 Bitcoin Fog 的创始人因帮助贩卖非法毒品的暗网市场洗钱数千万美元，在华盛顿联邦法院被判有罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/crypto-mixer-convicted-of-money-laundering-on-bitcoin-fog</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:28:53 GMT</pubDate>
